00:24:58.750 --> 00:25:02.870
But, Kidd was a desperate man, and historians believe that

00:25:02.870 --> 00:25:06.580
he had written this in the hope that it might save his life.

00:25:07.360 --> 00:25:13.080
It didn’t, and this treasure, if indeed it ever existed, has never been found.

